<Para>the SGML documents that make up a
book
</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>
a hypertext TOC for each book
</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>style sheet(s)
</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>a bookcase specification
</Para>
</ListItem>
